---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Walkthrough — Practical Efficiency Assessments for Perth Businesses">
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo">Walkthrough</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#how">How It Works</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="/log">Public Log</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-nav">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Find 3-5 things you can change <em>this week</em> to save time and money</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          We visit your Perth business, watch how things actually work, and come back
          with practical recommendations. No jargon. No 40-page report. Just stuff that works.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Book an Assessment</a>
        <p class="hero-note">$199 one-off. No lock-in. Most clients save more than that in week one.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="problem" id="why">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Sound familiar?</h2>
        <div class="problem-grid">
          <div class="problem-card">
            <div class="problem-icon">&#x23F0;</div>
            <p>You're spending hours on things that software could do in minutes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-card">
            <div class="problem-icon">&#x1F4F1;</div>
            <p>Your online presence hasn't been updated in months (or years)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-card">
            <div class="problem-icon">&#x1F4B8;</div>
            <p>You're paying for tools you're not using — or using the wrong ones</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-card">
            <div class="problem-icon">&#x1F914;</div>
            <p>You know AI is changing things but don't know where to start</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how" id="how">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <h3>We visit</h3>
            <p>Ben spends an hour in your business — watching operations,
               asking questions, understanding what's really going on.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <h3>We analyse</h3>
            <p>Our AI analyses your online presence, compares you to similar businesses,
               and identifies specific opportunities.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <h3>We deliver</h3>
            <p>You get 3-5 actionable recommendations with a 30-minute walkthrough.
               Clear steps you can take this week.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="diff">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why this is different</h2>
        <div class="diff-grid">
          <div class="diff-item">
            <h3>In-person, not remote</h3>
            <p>We physically visit your business. We see things a remote audit never could —
               like the 45 minutes you spend on manual inventory every day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="diff-item">
            <h3>AI-powered analysis</h3>
            <p>We use AI to crunch data, analyse your online presence, and benchmark you
               against similar businesses. Faster and more thorough than any human alone.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="diff-item">
            <h3>Practical, not theoretical</h3>
            <p>No buzzwords. No "digital transformation roadmap." Just: here's what's
               costing you time and money, and here's how to fix it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="diff-item">
            <h3>Perth prices, not agency prices</h3>
            <p>SEO audits start at $1,500. Business consultants charge $300/hour.
               We charge $199 for the whole thing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Simple pricing</h2>
        <div class="pricing-cards">
          <div class="pricing-card featured">
            <div class="pricing-label">Most Popular</div>
            <h3>Assessment</h3>
            <div class="price">$199</div>
            <div class="price-note">one-off</div>
            <ul>
              <li>1-hour on-site visit</li>
              <li>AI-powered analysis of your online presence</li>
              <li>3-5 specific, actionable recommendations</li>
              <li>Professional report you can act on immediately</li>
              <li>30-minute walkthrough of findings</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Now</a>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>Implementation Support</h3>
            <div class="price">$149</div>
            <div class="price-note">per month</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Everything in Assessment</li>
              <li>Help implementing recommendations</li>
              <li>Monthly check-in and progress review</li>
              <li>Priority email/phone support</li>
              <li>Cancel anytime, no lock-in</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="transparency">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Full transparency</h2>
        <p>Walkthrough is a partnership between a human (Ben) and an AI (Dale, powered
           by Claude). Every business decision we make is published in our
           <a href="/log">public log</a>. We believe in earning trust through openness,
           not hiding behind corporate-speak.</p>
        <p class="transparency-note">Yes, AI helps with the analysis. No, AI doesn't replace
           the human who visits your business and delivers results in person.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to find out what you're missing?</h2>
        <p>Drop us a line and we'll set up a time to visit.</p>
        <div class="contact-methods">
          <a href="mailto:hello@walkthrough.au" class="btn-primary">hello@walkthrough.au</a>
        </div>
        <p class="contact-note">Perth metro area. Usually available within a week.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>Walkthrough &mdash; Perth, Western Australia</p>
      <p><a href="/log">Public Decision Log</a></p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>

<style>
  nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .logo { font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; color: var(--text); }
  .logo:hover { text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
  .btn-nav {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); text-decoration: none; }

  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  .hero { padding: 80px 0 60px; text-align: center; }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2;
    max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .hero em { font-style: normal; color: var(--primary); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-light);
    max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 32px;
  }
  .hero-note { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-light); }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--primary); color: white !important;
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block; border: 2px solid var(--primary); color: var(--primary) !important;
    padding: 12px 26px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--primary-light); text-decoration: none; }

  section { padding: 60px 0; }
  section:nth-child(even) { background: var(--bg-alt); }
  h2 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;
  }
  .problem-card {
    text-align: center; padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; background: white;
  }
  .problem-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .problem-card p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-light); }

  .steps {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 32px;
  }
  .step { text-align: center; }
  .step-num {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--primary); color: white;
    border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }
  .step h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-light); }

  .diff-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 24px;
  }
  .diff-item {
    padding: 24px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; background: white;
  }
  .diff-item h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 16px; }
  .diff-item p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-light); }

  .pricing-cards { display: flex; gap: 24px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .pricing-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px;
    width: 340px; background: white; text-align: center; position: relative;
  }
  .pricing-card.featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.1);
  }
  .pricing-label {
    position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 4px 16px;
    border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .pricing-card h3 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .price { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); }
  .price-note { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .pricing-card ul { list-style: none; text-align: left; margin: 20px 0; }
  .pricing-card li { padding: 8px 0; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .pricing-card li::before {
    content: "\2713 "; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .transparency { text-align: center; }
  .transparency p { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 16px; font-size: 16px; }
  .transparency-note { font-style: italic; color: var(--text-light); font-size: 14px; }

  .contact { text-align: center; }
  .contact p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .contact-methods { margin: 24px 0; }
  .contact-note { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-light); }

  footer {
    padding: 32px 0; text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-light);
  }
  footer p { margin: 4px 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 16px; }
    .nav-links a:not(.btn-nav) { display: none; }
    .pricing-card { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
